Force Capital



Home







Force Capital















 Force Capital Management, LLC is registered as an investment advisor with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission.  Force Capital, headquartered in New York City, was founded in 2002 by Robert S. Jaffe, who continues to serve as Chief Investment Officer and oversees all investment activity.   Force Capital offers a variety of funds to financial institutions, pension plans, foundations, endowments, and other qualified investors. Force Capital employs a catalyst driven core U.S. long/short equity strategy in which it seeks to achieve superior, risk-adjusted and absolute returns across different market environments.  Force Capital undertakes a fundamental and intensive research approach to identify securities that demonstrate valuation discrepancies between current trading prices and intrinsic value, ordinarily accompanied by a catalyst for value recognition.  Copyright © 2014 Force Capital Management, LLC.  All rights reserved. Terms of Use





 


 


