Company Overview of Force Capital Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Force Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to banking or thrift institutions. It also caters to for high net worth individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, pooled investment vehicles, and charitable organizations. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. Force Capital Management is based in New York City with an additional office in Greenwich, Connecticut.


